&lt;p>Life is a process and in life we do processes &lt;br>
Something is given to us as an input &lt;br>
We do some actions on the given input &lt;br>
And we produce some output &lt;br>
Input is never 100% in our control. But, the quantity and quality of the benefits &lt;br>
depends upon how the output of a process &lt;br>
is perceived by the receiver.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>